          "content": "Sekarang saya sudah memahami konsepnya. Mari saya buat analisis dan konsep perbaikan untuk surat bebas pustaka:\n\n---\n\n## Analisis Perbandingan: Clearance Letter vs RPH Hafazan with Signatures\n\n### Masalah pada Clearance Letter Saat Ini:\n1. **QR Code menggunakan API eksternal** - `api.qrserver.com` (lambat, bergantung internet)\n2. **Tidak ada signature QR yang terenkripsi** - hanya link biasa\n3. **Layout terlalu banyak whitespace** - tidak efisien\n4. **Tidak ada badge status** yang jelas\n5. **Logo menggunakan file path langsung** - bisa gagal saat generate PDF\n\n### Keunggulan RPH Hafazan with Signatures:\n1. **QR Code di-generate lokal** menggunakan `simplesoftwareio/simple-qrcode` (SVG base64)\n2. **Signature QR berisi data terenkripsi** (hash MD5 untuk verifikasi)\n3. **Layout 2 kolom** yang efisien\n4. **Status badge** yang jelas\n5. **Logo di-convert ke base64** sebelum render PDF\n6. **Dual signature** (pembuat & approver)\n\n---\n\n## Konsep Perbaikan Surat Bebas Pustaka\n\nBerikut konsep yang saya rekomendasikan:\n\n### 1. Controller Baru\n```php\n// Tambahkan method generateSignatureQr di Model ClearanceLetter\npublic function generateLibrarianSignatureQr(): string\n{\n    $signatureData = [\n        'doc' => 'CLEARANCE',\n        'id' => $this->id,\n        'letter_no' => $this->letter_number,\n        'member' => $this->member->name,\n        'nim' => $this->member->member_id,\n        'approved_by' => $this->approver?->name,\n        'approved_at' => $this->approved_at?->timestamp,\n        'hash' => md5('CLEARANCE' . $this->id . $this->member_id)\n    ];\n\n    $qrCode = QrCode::format('svg')\n        ->size(200)\n        ->margin(1)\n        ->errorCorrection('H')\n        ->generate(json_encode($signatureData));\n\n    return 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,' . base64_encode($qrCode);\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Template PDF Baru (Konsep)\n- Layout lebih compact seperti RPH\n- QR signature dengan data terenkripsi\n- Logo base64\n- Status badge\n- Info card dengan border\n\nMau saya langsung implementasikan perbaikan ini ke file clearance-letter.blade.php dan controller-nya?"

->get();\n    }\n\n    public function render()\n    {\n        if (!$this->memberId) {\n            return view('livewire.my-submissions', [\n                'submissions' => collect(),\n                     "Text": "=== Operation 1 Result (Text) ===\n#  Deployment Guide - Laravel Perpustakaan to VM\n\n## Overview\n\n| Component | Size | Sync Method |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| Application Code | ~500MB | Git/rsync |\n| Main Database (SQLite) | 84KB | Direct copy |\n| Shamela Database | 21GB | rsync (background) |\n| Universitaria PDFs | 4.8GB | rsync (background) |\n| Book Databases | 672MB | rsync (background) |\n| Total Storage | ~28GB | rsync incremental |\n\n---\n\n##  Recommended Deployment Strategy\n\n### Phase 1: Application Deployment (15 min)\n\n```bash\n# 1. Clone/pull code on VM\ncd /var/www\ngit clone git@github.com:your-repo/perpustakaan.git\n# OR git pull if updating\n\n# 2. Install dependencies\ncd perpustakaan\ncomposer install --optimize-autoloader --no-dev\nnpm ci && npm run build\n\n# 3. Copy environment\ncp .env.example .env\nnano .env  # Configure production values\n\n# 4. Generate key & optimize\nphp artisan key:generate\nphp artisan config:cache\nphp artisan route:cache\nphp artisan view:cache\nphp artisan storage:link\n```\n\n### Phase 2: Database Sync (5 min)\n\n**Option A: Copy SQLite from Local (Recommended)**\n```bash\n# From local machine - main app database only\nscp database/database.sqlite user@vm:/var/www/perpustakaan/database/\n```\n\n**Option B: Fresh Migration + Seed**\n```bash\nphp artisan migrate --force\nphp artisan db:seed --force\n```\n\n### Phase 3: Large Files Sync (2-8 hours, background)\n\nUse the existing workflow: `/sync-large-files`\n\n```bash\n# From local machine, run in screen/tmux\nexport PROD_HOST=\"your-vm-ip\"\nexport PROD_USER=\"your-user\"\nexport PROD_PATH=\"/var/www/perpustakaan/storage\"\n\n# Start with Shamela (largest, run overnight)\nscreen -S shamela-sync\nrsync -avz --progress -e ssh \\\n  storage/database/shamela_content.db \\\n  storage/database/master.db \\\n  storage/database/cover.db \\\n  storage/database/book/ \\\n  $PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST:$PROD_PATH/database/\n\n# Ctrl+A, D to detach\n```\n\n---\n\n##  Pre-Deployment Checklist\n\n```bash\n# Local - Before deployment\n[ ] Backup production database\n[ ] Run tests: php artisan test\n[ ] Check composer audit: composer audit\n[ ] Commit all changes\n[ ] Tag release: git tag v1.x.x\n\n# VM - Environment\n[ ] PHP 8.2+ installed\n[ ] Required extensions: pdo, sqlite3, gd, mbstring, xml\n[ ] Composer installed\n[ ] Node.js 18+ installed\n[ ] Storage directories writable\n```\n\n---\n\n##  Production .env Template\n\n```env\nAPP_NAME=\"Perpustakaan UNIDA\"\nAPP_ENV=production\nAPP_DEBUG=false\nAPP_URL=https://perpustakaan.unida.gontor.ac.id\n\n# Database\nDB_CONNECTION=sqlite\n# OR for MySQL:\n# DB_CONNECTION=mysql\n# DB_HOST=127.0.0.1\n# DB_DATABASE=perpustakaan\n# DB_USERNAME=perpustakaan_user\n# DB_PASSWORD=secure_password\n\n# Session Security\nSESSION_DRIVER=database\nSESSION_ENCRYPT=true\nSESSION_SECURE_COOKIE=true\nSESSION_LIFETIME=120\n\n# Security\nADMIN_IP_RESTRICTION=true\nADMIN_ALLOWED_IPS=your.office.ip,another.ip\n```\n\n---\n\n##  Update/Maintenance Workflow\n\n```bash\n# Quick code update (no large files)\ncd /var/www/perpustakaan\ngit pull origin main\ncomposer install --optimize-autoloader --no-dev\nnpm ci && npm run build\nphp artisan migrate --force\nphp artisan config:cache\nphp artisan route:cache\nphp artisan view:cache\nphp artisan queue:restart\n```\n\n---\n\n##  Important Notes\n\n1. **Large files are NOT in git** - must sync via rsync\n2. **storage/database/** is gitignored - Shamela, Ebooks, etc.\n3. **Main SQLite** (84KB) contains app data - sync via scp\n4. **Run Shamela sync overnight** - 21GB takes 2-8 hours\n5. **Use incremental sync** - rsync only transfers changes\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# On VM after deployment\nphp artisan about\nphp artisan route:list | wc -l\ndu -sh storage/database/*\nsqlite3 database/database.sqlite \"SELECT COUNT(*) FROM users;\"\n```\n\n=== Operation 2 Result (Text) ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# =============================================================================\n# Deploy to Production VM\n# =============================================================================\n# Usage: ./scripts/deploy.sh [full|code|db|sync]\n#\n# Options:\n#   full  - Full deployment (code + database + large files)\n#   code  - Code only (git pull + composer + npm)\n#   db    - Sync main database only\n#   sync  - Sync large files (Shamela, Universitaria)\n# =============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\n# Configuration - EDIT THESE\nPROD_HOST=\"${PROD_HOST:-your-vm-ip}\"\nPROD_USER=\"${PROD_USER:-your-username}\"\nPROD_PATH=\"${PROD_PATH:-/var/www/perpustakaan}\"\nSSH_KEY=\"${SSH_KEY:-~/.ssh/id_rsa}\"\n\n# Colors\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nNC='\\033[0m' # No Color\n\necho_info() { echo -e \"${GREEN}[INFO]${NC} $1\"; }\necho_warn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}[WARN]${NC} $1\"; }\necho_error() { echo -e \"${RED}[ERROR]${NC} $1\"; }\n\n# Check SSH connection\ncheck_ssh() {\n    echo_info \"Checking SSH connection...\"\n    if ! ssh -i \"$SSH_KEY\" -o ConnectTimeout=5 \"$PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST\" \"echo 'connected'\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n        echo_error \"Cannot connect to $PROD_HOST\"\n        exit 1\n    fi\n    echo_info \"SSH connection OK\"\n}\n\n# Deploy code via git\ndeploy_code() {\n    echo_info \"Deploying code...\"\n    ssh -i \"$SSH_KEY\" \"$PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST\" << EOF\ncd $PROD_PATH\ngit pull origin main\ncomposer install --optimize-autoloader --no-dev\nnpm ci && npm run build\nphp artisan migrate --force\nphp artisan config:cache\nphp artisan route:cache\nphp artisan view:cache\nphp artisan queue:restart || true\necho \"Code deployment complete!\"\nEOF\n}\n\n# Sync main database\nsync_database() {\n    echo_info \"Syncing main database...\"\n    \n    # Backup remote first\n    ssh -i \"$SSH_KEY\" \"$PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST\" \\\n        \"cp $PROD_PATH/database/database.sqlite $PROD_PATH/database/database.sqlite.bak-\\$(date +%Y%m%d%H%M%S)\" || true\n    \n    # Copy local database\n    rsync -avz --progress \\\n        -e \"ssh -i $SSH_KEY\" \\\n        database/database.sqlite \\\n        \"$PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST:$PROD_PATH/database/\"\n    \n    echo_info \"Database sync complete!\"\n}\n\n# Sync large files\nsync_large_files() {\n    echo_info \"Syncing large files (this may take hours)...\"\n    echo_warn \"Running in background mode. Use 'screen -r' to monitor.\"\n    \n    # Shamela databases\n    echo_info \"Syncing Shamela database...\"\n    rsync -avz --progress --partial \\\n        -e \"ssh -i $SSH_KEY\" \\\n        storage/database/ \\\n        \"$PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST:$PROD_PATH/storage/database/\"\n    \n    # Public storage (universitaria, covers, etc)\n    echo_info \"Syncing public storage...\"\n    rsync -avz --progress --partial \\\n        -e \"ssh -i $SSH_KEY\" \\\n        --exclude='*.log' \\\n        storage/app/public/ \\\n        \"$PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST:$PROD_PATH/storage/app/public/\"\n    \n    echo_info \"Large files sync complete!\"\n}\n\n# Main\nmain() {\n    local mode=\"${1:-full}\"\n    \n    echo \"==========================================\"\n    echo \" Perpustakaan Deployment Script\"\n    echo \" Mode: $mode\"\n    echo \" Target: $PROD_USER@$PROD_HOST\"\n    echo \"==========================================\"\n    \n    check_ssh\n    \n    case \"$mode\" in\n        full)\n            deploy_code\n            sync_database\n            echo_warn \"Large files sync not included in 'full'. Run with 'sync' separately.\"\n            ;;\n        code)\n            deploy_code\n            ;;\n        db)\n            sync_database\n            ;;\n        sync)\n            sync_large_files\n            ;;\n        *)\n            echo \"Usage: $0 [full|code|db|sync]\"\n            exit 1\n            ;;\n    esac\n    \n    echo_info \"Deployment complete!\"\n}\n\nmain \"$@\""

    "> /model",
    "> Hai kiro coba kamu lihat surat bebas perpustakaan di project ini, dan peljari konsep download rph with signature di poroject tams, karena surat clerance bebas pustaka ini masih sangat berantakan, dan berat saat di download, buat konsep alur dan stylenya kurng lebih seperti rph hafazan with signature di tams view/pdf peljari dengan baik teliti dan presisi",
    "Saya perlu melihat struktur project ini dulu untuk menemukan file surat bebas perpustakaan, dan juga melihat project TAMS untuk mempelajari konsep RPH with signature.\n[Tool uses: fs_read,fs_read]",
    "> t",
    "Saya menemukan project TAMS di `/Library/WebServer/web-server/tams`. Sekarang saya akan mencari file surat bebas perpustakaan di project perpustakaan dan file RPH with signature di project TAMS.\n[Tool uses: fs_read,fs_read,grep]",
    "Sekarang saya akan melihat file clearance-letter.blade.php di perpustakaan dan mencari file RPH hafazan with signature di TAMS.\n[Tool uses: fs_read,grep,fs_read]",
    "> t",
    "Bagus! Sekarang saya akan melihat file RPH Hafazan with Signatures di TAMS untuk mempelajari konsepnya:\n[Tool uses: fs_read,fs_read]",
    "Sekarang saya akan melihat model RphHafazan untuk memahami bagaimana QR signature dihasilkan:\n[Tool uses: grep]",
    "\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
    "Sekarang saya sudah memahami konsepnya. Mari saya buat analisis dan konsep perbaikan untuk surat bebas pustaka:\n\n---\n\n## Analisis Perbandingan: Clearance Letter vs RPH Hafazan with Signatures\n\n### Masalah pada Clearance Letter Saat Ini:\n1. **QR Code menggunakan API eksternal** - `api.qrserver.com` (lambat, bergantung internet)\n2. **Tidak ada signature QR yang terenkripsi** - hanya link biasa\n3. **Layout terlalu banyak whitespace** - tidak efisien\n4. **Tidak ada badge status** yang jelas\n5. **Logo menggunakan file path langsung** - bisa gagal saat generate PDF\n\n### Keunggulan RPH Hafazan with Signatures:\n1. **QR Code di-generate lokal** menggunakan `simplesoftwareio/simple-qrcode` (SVG base64)\n2. **Signature QR berisi data terenkripsi** (hash MD5 untuk verifikasi)\n3. **Layout 2 kolom** yang efisien\n4. **Status badge** yang jelas\n5. **Logo di-convert ke base64** sebelum render PDF\n6. **Dual signature** (pembuat & approver)\n\n---\n\n## Konsep Perbaikan Surat Bebas Pustaka\n\nBerikut konsep yang saya rekomendasikan:\n\n### 1. Controller Baru\n```php\n// Tambahkan method generateSignatureQr di Model ClearanceLetter\npublic function generateLibrarianSignatureQr(): string\n{\n    $signatureData = [\n        'doc' => 'CLEARANCE',\n        'id' => $this->id,\n        'letter_no' => $this->letter_number,\n        'member' => $this->member->name,\n        'nim' => $this->member->member_id,\n        'approved_by' => $this->approver?->name,\n        'approved_at' => $this->approved_at?->timestamp,\n        'hash' => md5('CLEARANCE' . $this->id . $this->member_id)\n    ];\n\n    $qrCode = QrCode::format('svg')\n        ->size(200)\n        ->margin(1)\n        ->errorCorrection('H')\n        ->generate(json_encode($signatureData));\n\n    return 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,' . base64_encode($qrCode);\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Template PDF Baru (Konsep)\n- Layout lebih compact seperti RPH\n- QR signature dengan data terenkripsi\n- Logo base64\n- Status badge\n- Info card dengan border\n\nMau saya langsung implementasikan perbaikan ini ke file clearance-letter.blade.php dan controller-nya?\n[Tool uses: none]",
    "> Iya implementasikan, ada 2 QR juga ya 1. Mahasiswa yang megnajukan suratnya, 2. yang megnesahkan dan approve tugas akhirnya.",

    "Semua sudah selesai. Berikut ringkasan perubahan yang sudah diimplementasikan:\n\n---\n\n##  Implementasi Selesai\n\n### 1. Model `ClearanceLetter.php`\nDitambahkan 2 method untuk generate QR signature:\n- `generateMemberSignatureQr()` - QR untuk mahasiswa pengaju\n- `generateApproverSignatureQr()` - QR untuk pustakawan yang approve\n\nSetiap QR berisi data terenkripsi:\n- Document type, ID, letter number\n- Nama & NIM mahasiswa\n- Timestamp\n- Hash MD5 untuk verifikasi\n\n### 2. Controller `ClearanceLetterController.php`\n- Generate kedua QR signature sebelum render PDF\n- Convert logo ke base64 (tidak bergantung file path saat render)\n\n### 3. Template `clearance-letter.blade.php`\nPerubahan signifikan:\n- **Layout lebih compact** - margin dikurangi, font size dioptimalkan\n- **QR Code lokal** - tidak lagi pakai API eksternal (lebih cepat)\n- **Dual signature** - kiri: Mahasiswa, kanan: Pustakawan\n- **Status badge** - menunjukkan status \"Disetujui\"\n- **Style konsisten** dengan RPH Hafazan TAMS\n- **Logo base64** - tidak gagal saat generate PDF\n\n### Perbandingan Ukuran File (Estimasi)\n| Sebelum | Sesudah |\n|---------|---------|\n| ~500KB+ (API QR eksternal) | ~50-100KB (SVG base64 lokal) |\n\nPDF sekarang akan jauh lebih ringan dan cepat di-generate karena tidak perlu request ke server eksternal untuk QR code.\n[Tool uses: none]",
